org.gvsig.symbology.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.symbol.marker

Interface IMarkerSymbol

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CartographicSupport, Cloneable, IPrintable, ISymbol, Persistent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IChartSymbol, IMultiChartSymbol, IMultiLayerMarkerSymbol, IPictureMarkerSymbol, ISimpleMarkerSymbol
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMarkerSymbol, ArrowMarkerSymbol, CharacterMarkerSymbol, ChartSymbol, LinkedChartSymbol, MultiLayerMarkerSymbol, MultiShapeSymbol, PictureMarkerSymbol, SimpleMarkerSymbol, WarningSymbol

    public interface IMarkerSymbol
extends ISymbol, CartographicSupport
    Represents an ISymbol that draws a marker symbol.It has the different methods to obtain or define the attributes of a marker such as rotation, offset, size, color and IMask.
